[SHORT DESC]
A Ball used to catch Pokemon that is more effective against lower level Pokemon.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>A type of Ball used to catch Pokemon. Cannot be used during Trainer, Link, or Wi-Fi Battles.</p>

<p>The capture rate modifier changes depending on the relative levels of the Trainer's and wild Pokemon. If the level of the wild Pokemon is:</p>
<ul>
<li>The same or higher: *1</li>
<li>Lower: *2</li>
<li>Half or less: *4</li>
<li>A quarter or less: *8</li>
</ul>